1528 // will not work when:
1529 //    1) SCEV traces back to an instruction inside the loop that SCEV can not
1530 // expand, eg. add %indvar, (load %addr)
1531 //    2) SCEV finds a loop variant, eg. add %indvar, %loopvariant
